&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://planet.opendocumentformat.org/"&gt;* Leia mais no Planeta ODF....&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 May 2010 23:46:40 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/odf-open-document-format-comemora-5-anos</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/odf-open-document-format-comemora-5-anos</guid></item><item><title>Vem aí o Document Freedom Day DFD 2010 - 31 Março - Curitiba</title><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: xx-large;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #339900;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.documentfreedom.org/Gubro-PR" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img src="http://www.softwarelivreparana.org.br/uploads/img4ba29c51f300f.png" height="309" alt="" width="437"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
